summary: This document is an external email calendar invitation for a call regarding Maxwell photo metadata, scheduled for May 3, 2021. It involves personnel from the US Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS) and the FBI, indicating coordination on evidentiary matters in the Ghislaine Maxwell case.

events.title: Call re Maxwell photo metadata

keyFacts: A call was scheduled for May 3, 2021, to discuss photo metadata evidence related to Ghislaine Maxwell.
The call involved coordination between the US Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS) and the FBI.
The document is an external email calendar invitation, indicating formal planning for evidence review.
The event was classified as 'X-PERSONAL' and given a high priority level of 5.
